{"tid":2074182,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"中國自主研發高速磁浮列車測試成功，時速高達 600 公里，直迫日本JR東海L0 磁浮新幹線","createTime":"2020-06-22T02:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T06:53:12.000Z","uid":109923,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"b938be2119c7e99f10279d569a28b450d0e54ea8","tid":2074182,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"　　中國在發展高速列車方面一直有投放不少資源，最近中車四方就成功測試新的高速磁浮列車，時速高達 600 公里，將對未來的磁浮列車開發帶來重要的示範作用。<br />\n<br />\n　　今次的開發計劃是由中車四方股份公司負責，在上海同濟大學磁浮試驗線首次試驗成功，據稱測試內容包括懸浮導向、測速定位、車軌耦合、地面牽引、車地通信等多個範疇，在使用不同軌道梁以及道岔、小曲線、坡道、分區切換等情況下進行測試。副總工程師丁叁叁表示，各項關鍵技術指標符合設計要求，達到設計預期。<br />\n<br />\n　　據中車四方表示，高速磁浮列車的工程樣本將會在 2020 年底完成，然後可以開始建設示範路段等開發，進一步為高速磁浮工程帶來穩固的發展基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　現在除了中國開發高速磁浮列車之外，日本 JR 東海也已經在 2015 年成功測試旗下 L0 磁浮列車，當時最高速度達到時速 603 公里，預計會在 2027 年完成中央新幹線連接東京和名古屋。<br />\n<br />\n2015年曝光至今，不斷測試中的日本JR東海 L0 磁浮新幹線<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qAlmBSF8AO4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqAlmBSF8AO4&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=679cc4e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qAlmBSF8AO4</a><br />\n<br />\n　　2020年9月起，日本JR東將試運行 L0 磁浮新幹線，正式標誌始於1962年的磁懸浮技術歷經50年的研究已逐漸走向成熟。此外，時速高達400公里的次世代新幹線Alfa-X也將於2022年投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbCXFmJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbCXFmJ.jpg&h=1c3010ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6UCFmJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6UCFmJ.jpg&h=c4eff5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coK7h8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoK7h8p.jpg&h=37a8ebfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CQuwtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CQuwtp.jpg&h=5e019905&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5c1800c791e3b64f49b7807903c0abb36c5417d","tid":2074182,"uid":78971,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勁呀中國<br />\n又多一樣野可以擠身國際<br />\n2020繼續強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c75415ebeb84413c5a820168dcba03ba33abdeb","tid":2074182,"uid":358542,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"日本都要研究50年既技術，中國竟然做到，而且仲要咁岩係衣家呢個不穩局勢公怖出來"},{"pid":"e4458118c7a2e17e4e4f04d8560781aa15573e2d","tid":2074182,"uid":147367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:22:59.000Z","msg":"高速地獄列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284168c3a4194f7ed6f8ad513bf542e7cb031e50","tid":2074182,"uid":254865,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"溫州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fde4a6807edf387cc9301bcc448cfddc572366","tid":2074182,"uid":63157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等睇出事"},{"pid":"089969a3d4c6db600d05fa6fe82c7ead4080ff87","tid":2074182,"uid":309753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:25:28.000Z","msg":"車毀人亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b19bad0f5b2db76f64e8602e2503b1607eccdc5","tid":2074182,"uid":73569,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"改返個靚名最緊要<br />\n死亡號列車"},{"pid":"e78a2c23caf2c1d1032ad43412f1d2288e5d4c84","tid":2074182,"uid":30678,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTim